If clalev([F:ATZ]) : Close File [ATZ] : Endif
If clalev([F:ATI]) : Close File [ATI] : Endif

Local File AVIEWTAB [ATB]
Local File AVIEWFLD [ATZ]
Local File AVIEWIND [ATI]
Return


